%F A029916 a(n+1143) = a(n) + 1250.
%F A029916 G.f.: (P(x)*(1-x) + 1250*x^1143)/((1-x)*(1-x^1143)), where P(x) = Sum_{n=0..1142} a(n)*x^n. (End)
